# Post-Edit Verification

After editing any `.ts` or `.tsx` file in `src/`:

1. Run **`pnpm check`** (Biome: `biome check`)
2. Run **`pnpm test`** (Vitest)

Fix any reported issues — do not consider the task complete until both pass for the touched areas.

For DOM/component tests, use `// @vitest-environment jsdom` at the top of the file when the test needs a browser-like environment (see existing `*.test.tsx` files).
